sequenceDiagram
    participant TIMER as 5-min Timer<br/>(barCloseTs + 50ms)
    participant BB as bar-builder.ts
    participant EB as Atlas Event Bus
    participant FE as feature-engine.ts
    participant PB as processBar()
    participant ADE as ADE
    participant ARI as ARI
    participant TVL as TVL
    participant GRD as Guardian/Safety
    participant TP as tpDispatch.ts
    participant DB_MEM as atlas_memory
    participant SSE as SSE Fan-Out

    TIMER->>BB: Bar window closed
    BB->>BB: Finalise confirmed bar<br/>{ open, high, low, close, volume, tickCount }
    BB->>EB: AtlasBarEvent { status: confirmed }

    EB->>FE: AtlasBarEvent confirmed
    FE->>FE: Calculate ATR, ADX, RSI<br/>VWAP, EMAs, Regime
    FE->>EB: AtlasBarEvent { status: confirmed, indicators: {...} }

    EB->>PB: AtlasBarEvent with indicators
    PB->>ADE: Evaluate entry conditions
    ADE-->>PB: Decision { direction, confidence }
    PB->>ARI: Validate risk parameters
    ARI-->>PB: Approved / Rejected
    PB->>TVL: Check position limits
    TVL-->>PB: Status
    PB->>GRD: Safety checks
    GRD-->>PB: Clear / Block

    alt Signal approved
        PB->>TP: Dispatch order
        TP->>TP: POST TradersPost webhook
    end

    PB->>DB_MEM: INSERT atlas_memory (confirmed bar + indicators)
    EB->>SSE: AtlasBarEvent confirmed
    SSE->>SSE: Broadcast atlas_bar_confirmed to all clients

    Note over BB,SSE: Total latency target: < 200ms from bar close to processBar()
